14 // Update the description of Denver, in the City table that is a non-versioned table.  workspace . PerformOperation ( true ,   esriMultiuserEditSessionMode . esriMESMNonVersioned , 
    ()= 
    { 
        var   cities   =   workspace . GetTable ( typeof ( City )); 
        var   filter   =   new   QueryFilter (); 
        filter . Where   =   City =  Denver ; 

         var   denver   =   cities . Map City ( filter ). SingleOrDefault (); 
         denver . Description   =   The capital of Colorado. ; 
         denver . Update (); 

         return   true ;   // Commit the operation. 
     });

When editing a version table or feature class, you can take the same actions as above, except specify the versioned enumeration.   1
